{"tid":539804,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"窮jj 又問車","createTime":"2018-01-25T01:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T14:33:39.000Z","uid":10660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9657c0557f78e213938044a9521db83851a2efba","tid":539804,"uid":10660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T01:39:09.000Z","msg":"之前問過而自己最後搵左幾款<br />\n但唔知點比較<br />\nToyota RAV4<br />\nLexus RX300<br />\nToyota Harrier（水貨RX300）<br />\nSienta<br />\n<br />\n 筆直7萬內<br />\n上邊三架SUV 都只可以買到06-07年<br />\n而Sienta 可以買到G版07-09 年<br />\n<br />\n個人使用方面安全優先，其次維修費油費<br />\nRAV4 睇過好似8 氣袋，另外兩架唔知<br />\nSienta 應該2 氣袋，但有d 人又話有4 氣袋<br />\n<br />\n駕駛方面安全駕駛第一，唔快車，唔鬥車<br />\n錫車，雖然勤保養但多數搞d 自己搞到嘅野，例如洗車換風隔洗冷氣換水箱水，買d 乜乜保養劑得閒噴下咁。<br />\n<br />\n請各位指導下窮jj<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273bcab9cb27b93d1ee73f9194f1798297a40253","tid":539804,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T01:39:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36268fbf53633abc6054564f9b10405b7c8a2050","tid":539804,"uid":15199,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"273bcab9cb27b93d1ee73f9194f1798297a40253","tid":539804,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T01:39:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T01:46:49.000Z","msg":"過主啦"},{"pid":"e8bbc8b254a7cadb94d87ad05e6f3b1ad94b78aa","tid":539804,"uid":166751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"273bcab9cb27b93d1ee73f9194f1798297a40253","tid":539804,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T01:39:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T11:02:40.000Z","msg":"搵你老母"},{"pid":"3670f15ca6efcb021ed047450d62d8d010f50125","tid":539804,"uid":10133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"273bcab9cb27b93d1ee73f9194f1798297a40253","tid":539804,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T01:39:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"c